Pasos:
1. git clone <https://github.com/harbour/core> harbour
2. Construir Harbour asi: go64.bat

call "%ProgramFiles(x86)%\Microsoft Visual Studio\2019\Community\VC\Auxiliary\Build\vcvarsall.bat" x86_amd64
set HB_BUILD_MODE=c
set HB_USER_PRGFLAGS=-l-
set HB_BUILD_CONTRIBS=
set HB_WITH_OPENSSL=c:\OpenSSL-Win32\include
set HB_WITH_CURL=c:\curl\include
del .\src\common\obj\win\msvc64\hbver.obj
del .\src\common\obj\win\msvc64\hbver_dyn.obj
del .\src\common\obj\win\msvc\hbverdsp.obj
win-make.exe
3. crear carpeta c:\harbour\contrib\modharbour\  (esto puede hacerse después del paso 1)
4. copiar los ficheros modharbour.hbp, mod.hbp, apache.prg y mod_harbour.c en esa carpeta
5.  desde c:\harbour\contrib\modharbour\ ejecutar este go64.bat

call "%ProgramFiles(x86)%\Microsoft Visual Studio\2019\Community\VC\Auxiliary\Build\vcvarsall.bat" x86_amd64
..\..\bin\win\msvc64\hbmk2 modharbour
